name: color-me
description: ## The making of #mood Pearl Hacks 2018 was my second time at the UNC hackathon. The previous year I had made [Lukewarm Greeting Cards](http://dainryoo.github.io/lukewarm/) and was very proud of myself for 1) successfully completing something and 2) making something fun and having fun! So I aimed to do the same this year.
